We haven't contacted
with them for a long time.

634
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,560
Chunhui High School is

635
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:35,960
a good school.

636
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:39,000
It's a rare chance for the kid.

637
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,360
I know.

638
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:41,240
Ji Family wants

639
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:43,840
to do something for us.

640
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,480
I'm just afraid...

641
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:47,040
