650
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:07,640
What favor?

651
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:09,920
Never mind.

652
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:10,720
Anyway,

653
00:34:10,720 --> 00:34:12,600
as she's transferred here,

654
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,440
I invite her over to live with us.

655
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:16,560
It's kind of returning the favor.

656
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,120
She'll live here for a long time.

657
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,360
It's inconvenient for me.

658
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:22,520
She's a girl.

659
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:23,920
Even she didn't say it's inconvenient.

660
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:26,080
Why is it so inconvenient
for a boy like you?

661
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,720
Let me tell you this.

662
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,440
She's staying with us now.

663
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:31,480
