665
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:33,520
Do you hear me?

666
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,880
Or I'll hold you responsible.

667
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:02,840
You must be Ji Junxing's baby brother.

668
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:04,720
You're more lovely than your brother.

669
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:18,280
So comfortable.

670
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,280
Can I come in?

671
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:24,640
Sure.

672
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:28,960
Hello, Aunt.

673
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,360
Have a seat.

674
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:32,120
I've got you some fruits.

675
00:35:32,120 --> 00:35:32,960
Thank you, Aunt.

676
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,240
Aunt, please sit.

677
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:35,120
