678
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:36,160
Sit.

679
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:38,600
Lin Xi,

680
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:39,680
make yourself comfortable.

681
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:41,000
Just make

