with each other yet.

695
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,160
Ji Junxing is

696
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,600
like fried yoghurt.

697
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:15,080
On the outside,

698
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:17,240
