to get along with.

699
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,680
In fact, I know

700
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:20,360
that he's soft-hearted.

701
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,040
I also sincerely hope

702
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:24,000
