708
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,160
If you

709
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:35,920
need his help,

710
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:37,680
just knock on his door.

711
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,400
Don't worry about troubling him.

712
00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:40,920
Rest assured. Will do.

713
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:42,920
Okay.

